This is typically problematic in terms of application links, but various other features can break in relation to that (gadget feeds, issue links between JIRA and Confluence, macro browser, etc). A documentation would be needed to list all the steps required for the two products migrated together would keep working after going self-hosted. Purely loading the two backups and setting up application links will not work in most of the cases.

